how to watch the changes in the compiled file so that you dont have to tsc again and again when the .ts file has been modified
    use tsc <file_name> --watch
    after that you can just type following in the CLI
    node file_name.js

Variable Declaration:
    let and const keywords.
    let: 
        1)  Can be declared without being initialized.
        2)  Can be assigned a new value.

    const:
        1)  Needs to always be initialized while being declared.
        2)  cannot be assigned a new value.
  
    global and function scope
